    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">- Fix |arpeggio-commands| to behave the same as |:map| commands.&nbsp;&nbsp;In other words, &quot; and keys after &quot; in {rhs} for |arpeggio-commands| are treated as a part of {rhs}.&nbsp;&nbsp;Old versions don't behave so.<br>- Fix minor bugs.<br>- Revise the document a bit.<br>- Revise additional syntax highlighting a bit.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=9622">vim-arpeggio-0.0.5.zip</a></td>
