    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">- Add syntax highlighting for |arpeggio-commands|.<br>- Fix bugs of &quot;noremap&quot; version of |arpeggio-commands| such as<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;|:Arpeggionoremap| that {rhs} are remapped despite the meaning of<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;the commands.&nbsp;&nbsp;(Thanks for id:ampmmn)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=9466">vim-arpeggio-0.0.3.zip</a></td>
